data.description: Nicely updated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 4-level home with room for expansion in the Unfinished Basement. Located on a 0.17 acre lot in the Fountain neighborhood of Cross Creek at Mesa Ridge. Spacious floor plan with vaulted ceilings. Central air and heat for year round comfort. 2018 roof. Beautiful wood laminate floors through the Living Room, Dining Room., Family Room, and Primary Bedroom. The Living Room has high vaulted ceilings and a large window that brings in abundant light. It flows seamlessly into the Dining Room, making it a great area for entertaining and family get togethers. The Updated Kitchen features an attractive tile floor and white shaker cabinets with solid surface countertops. Stainless steel appliances include a smooth top range oven, built-in microwave, dishwasher, and French door refrigerator. Snuggle up to the gas log fireplace in the lower level Family Room on cold Colorado evenings. There is a powder bath and laundry closet on the lower level with washer that stays. The upper level hosts 3 Bedrooms, and 2 Full Baths. The Owner's Suite has a lighted ceiling fan, walk in closet, and adjoining 5pc bathrom. The bathroom features a dual sink vanity, soaking tub, and separate shower. Two more Bedrooms share a Full Bathroom with vanity, mirror, and tub/shower. 3-car attached garage with door opener. The large fenced backyard offers a stamped concrete patio for outdoor dining and relaxation. The level lot is well maintained and a great place for outdoor entertaining and family fun. Located close to schools, parks, shopping and restaurants. Convenient to Fort Carson and all military installations. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home!
